            <p>The sarcophagus of <persName xml:lang="grc " ref="persons.xml#caes0153p01">Arkadios </persName> and the <rs type="family">children </rs> of <persName xml:lang="grc " ref="persons.xml#caes0153p02">Eutropia</persName>, by <persName xml:lang="grc " ref="persons.xml#caes0153p03">Panagios</persName>.
		  </p>
         </div>
